OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784812719
OL,3,C'Mid-air 10-person brawl' forces UK-
OL,4,Cbound easyJet flight to return to
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,FA mid-air brawl involving around 10
OL,8,Fpassengers forced a Liverpool-bound
OL,9,FeasyJet plane to fly back to Tenerife,
OL,10,Faccording to air traffic control.
OL,12,FThe captain decided to return to Spain
OL,13,Fabout 30 minutes after departure "due
OL,14,Fto the danger" the fight "posed to the
OL,15,Fsafety of the flight", the air traffic
OL,16,Fcontroller said.
OL,18,FPolice met flight EZY3352 when it
OL,19,Ftouched down at Tenerife South airport
OL,20,Fon Tuesday evening, per the crew's
OL,21,Frequest.
OL,26,@uD@bOUvD@NO]vD@ZOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
