PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784812719
OL,3,C'Mid-air 10-person brawl' forces UK-
OL,4,Cbound easyJet flight to return to
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,FThe 186-passenger aircraft then
OL,8,Fcontinued to Liverpool.
OL,10,FThe air traffic controller said in its
OL,11,Fstatement, originally written in
OL,12,FSpanish: "Our full support goes out to
OL,13,Fthe crews and passengers who are
OL,14,Fincreasingly having to endure these
OL,15,Fsituations."
OL,17,FEasyJet said the plane "returned to
OL,18,Fthe airport and was met by police due
OL,19,Fto a group of passengers behaving
OL,20,Fdisruptively.
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@LO]yD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784812719
OL,3,C'Mid-air 10-person brawl' forces UK-
OL,4,Cbound easyJet flight to return to
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,F"The flight then continued to
OL,8,FLiverpool."
OL,10,FThe airline added: "Our cabin and
OL,11,Fground crew are trained to assess all
OL,12,Fsituations and to act quickly and
OL,13,Fappropriately to ensure that the
OL,14,Fsafety of the flight and other
OL,15,Fcustomers is not compromised at any
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,F"We take these incidents very
OL,19,Fseriously and do not tolerate
OL,20,Fdisruptive behaviour towards our staff.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]rD@TOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
