PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784812719
OL,3,C'Mid-air 10-person brawl' forces UK-
OL,4,Cbound easyJet flight to return to
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,F"The safety and wellbeing of customers
OL,8,Fand crew is always our highest
OL,9,Fpriority."
OL,11,FAir traffic control also said: "The
OL,12,Fcrew of the flight from Tenerife South
OL,13,Fto Liverpool, after about 30 minutes
OL,14,Fof flight, informed us that they
OL,15,Fneeded to return to the airport and
OL,16,Frequested police presence upon arrival.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@JO]sD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
