OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784812719
OL,3,C'Mid-air 10-person brawl' forces UK-
OL,4,Cbound easyJet flight to return to
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,F"A group of about 10 passengers had
OL,8,Fstarted a fight on board, and the
OL,9,Fcaptain decided to return due to the
OL,10,Fdanger it posed to the safety of the
OL,11,Fflight.
OL,13,F"We expedited their return as much as
OL,14,Fpossible while coordinating with the
OL,15,Fairport for police presence.
OL,17,F"They landed and cleared runway 07
OL,18,Fwithout incident."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOUzD@RO]
